item.title: CVE-2019-11897|2024-09-17T03:55:02.429Z -- prosyst -- mbs%20sdk
item.description: A Server-Side Request Forgery (SSRF) vulnerability in the backup & restore functionality in earlier versions than ProSyst mBS SDK 8.2.6 and Bosch IoT Gateway Software 9.3.0 allows a remote attacker to forge GET requests to arbitrary URLs. In addition, this could potentially allow an attacker to read sensitive zip files from the local server.
